e-eilish-and-bring-me-the-horizon-collab-on-the-way-3569124">Billie Eilish</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/it-looks-like-a-bring-me-the-horizon-and-underoath-collaboration-is-on-the-way-3569048">合作拍摄</a>《POST HUMAN: NeX GEn》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bring-me-the-horizon-bring-out-sleep-tokens-iv-for-antivist-in-australia-3705653">《Watch Bring Me The Horizo​​n》在澳大利亚推出 Sleep Token 的《Antivist》 IV</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
帕蒂·史密斯回应泰勒·斯威夫特在《折磨诗人部》中的名字检查https://www.nme.com/news/music/patti-smith-responds-to-taylor-swift-name-check-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3703931?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=patti-史密斯回应泰勒·斯威夫特名字检查受折磨的诗人部门Emma WilkesSat, 20 Apr 2024 12:55:46 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3703931 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特和帕蒂·史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>史密斯和受人尊敬的诗人迪伦·托马斯一起出现在专辑的主打歌中</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/patti-smith-responds-to-taylor-swift-name-check-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3703931">帕蒂·史密斯 (Patti Smith) 回应泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在“受折磨的诗人部门”中的名字检查的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特和帕蒂·史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/taylor-swift-patti-smith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/patti-smith">帕蒂·史密斯</a>对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-why-taylor-swift-name-drops-patti-smith-and-dylan-thomas-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3620037">将她的名字插入</a>她的新专辑《The Tortured Poets Department》的主打歌做出了回应。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</a></strong></li></ul><p>在歌曲中，斯威夫特在歌词中提到了史密斯和诗人迪伦·托马斯：“<em>我当着你的面嘲笑说，‘你不是迪伦·托马斯，我不是帕蒂·史密斯/这不是切尔西酒店/我们是现代白痴</em>。”</p><p>人们认为，主打歌指的是她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975 年乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">Matty Healy</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-music-undergoes-streaming-rise-amid-reports-of-taylor-swift-romance-3443019">短暂关系</a>，而她对史密斯和迪伦的评论则指的是 1975 年的主唱和她自己，因为这两个人不应该如此认真地对待自己，他们是据<a href="https://www.today.com/popculture/music/patti-smith-dylan-thomas-tortured-poets-department-taylor-swift-rcna148511" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《今日》</em></a>报道，他们只是“现代白痴”。</p><p>现在，史密斯在社交媒体上发表了一张她读《托马斯》的照片，对歌曲中出现她的名字一事发表了自己的看法。 “这就是说，我很高兴能在伟大的威尔士诗人迪伦·托马斯的陪伴下被提及。谢谢泰勒。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C59kqTfp6lF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; heigh