ploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/record-store-day-benjamin-cremel-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>今天（4 月 20 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">唱片店日</a>迎来了第 17 届，歌迷们从凌晨起就开始排队，等待从当地独立唱片店购买特别版唱片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2024-full-list-releases-vinyl-3588062">2024 年唱片店日：查看完整发行列表</a></strong></li></ul><p>一些大牌乐队为这一年度活动推出了特别的一次性收藏黑胶唱片和磁带，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daft-punk">Daft Punk</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heads">Talking Heads</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/talking-heADS">Paramore</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">Lily Allen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">Paramore</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">Noel Gallagher 的 High Flying鸟儿</a>。</p><p>金斯顿的宴会唱片公司在他们的社交媒体上表示，唱片店日大使<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">帕拉摩尔</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-byrne">大卫·伯恩</a>的分手是迄今为止最受欢迎的特别版本。其中包括 Paramore <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-paramores-return-with-cover-of-talking-heads-burning-down-the-house-3579806">翻唱的 Talking Heads 的《Burning Down The House》，</a>而 Byrne 翻唱了他们的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-byrne-to-cover-paramores-hard-times-for-record-store-day-2024-3597053">《Hard Times》。</a> </p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"><img src="htt